article.headline: Middle Tennessee 94, Trevecca Nazarene 53
article.story: TOWSON, Md. -- Kevin Kanaskie scored 22 points and Desmond Yates added 20 to help Middle Tennessee rout Trevecca Nazarene 94-53 on Friday night. Eric Allen also chipped in 12 for the Blue Raiders (1-0), who ran out to 46-24 lead at halftime. Kanaskie was 6-for-6 from behind the arc, and Middle Tennessee shot 64.4 percent from the field en route to victory. Jeremy Dixon paced the Trojans (0-1) with 12 points and Christopher Harris added nine more. The Trojans committed 25 turnovers and shot 43.8 percent from th field. The Blue Raiders had four players in double figures.
